# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Blue-Green Deployment

🔥 Modern DevOps deployment strategy.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

Updating live application directly is risky.

If update fails:

❌ downtime
❌ broken app

---

## Solution

Maintain TWO environments.

---

## 🔹 Blue Environment

Current live version.

---

## 🔹 Green Environment

New updated version.

---

## Deployment Flow

```text id="4m9xpk"
Users → Blue (old)

Test Green (new)

Switch traffic → Green
```

---

## Benefits

✔ near-zero downtime
✔ easy rollback
✔ safer deployments

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Opening new bridge before closing old bridge.

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why blue-green deployment useful?**

👉 It enables safe updates with minimal downtime and easy rollback.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="9v2qmn"
Two environments = safe switching
```

