# 🧠 OS Concept 2: Distributed Tracing

🔥 Important observability concept.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

One user request may pass through:

* API gateway
* authentication service
* database
* notification service

Hard to debug.

---

## Solution

Track full request journey.

👉 Distributed tracing

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Tracking parcel movement across delivery centers.

---

## Why Important?

✔ debugging
✔ latency analysis
✔ bottleneck detection

---

## Trace Example

```text id="5x8qrd"
Request A
 → Service 1
 → Service 2
 → Database
```

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why distributed tracing important?**

👉 Because requests travel across many services in distributed systems.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="3k7mwt"
Trace request across all services
```

