## 1️⃣ Traditional Computing

Uses electrons for computation.

---

# Photonic Computing

Uses light (photons) instead of electrons.

---

## Why Interesting?

Light can provide:

✔ faster communication
✔ lower heat
✔ high bandwidth

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

